Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.62,0:00:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,大家注意
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.87,0:00:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,集训地点确定是去温泉了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.96,0:00:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,还真突然
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.42,0:00:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,来
