Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.75,0:01:45.87,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}从明天到未来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.04,0:01:48.75,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}是啊 时间 Nonstop
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.96,0:01:54.55,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}先前烦恼的事情 通通都消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.71,0:02:00.43,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}来展开新的故事吧
